::Hot Rod::

He had done as he was told. He had took off for the base. Good thing it wasn&#39;t too far.

He pulled up in front of the base, and transformed to bot mode, holding the pod. He ran into the base, and too the bridge.

Once he arrived he put the pod down.

&quot;I dont know who has the know how to help this thing, but it needs energy and repair now! I have to get some energon and head back out. We found enought pod.&quot;

With that Hot Rod headed to the Mess Hall, grabbed a lot of energon, and made his way out of the base again.

He transformed and headed back at the other pod.

